&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Named Nurse for Children Looked After&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 8a&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated Named Nurse for Children Looked After who is able to support the strategic Children Looked After (CLA) agenda for Croydon Health Service NHS Trust .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work as part of the innovative Croydon Health Integrated Safeguarding Team to support the Head of Safeguarding and the Designated Professionals for CLA as part of a team delivering against statutory guidance on the health and wellbeing of Looked After Children on behalf of Croydon Health Services NHS Trust .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holders will work to ensure that the Trust achieve their commissioned functions for CLA services and that the quality and effectiveness of services provided meet the needs of Children Looked After.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews: tbc&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Jen Sarsby, Head of Safeguarding and Children Looked After&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;on 07785512326 or jen.sarsby1@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
